Value Filldown VRF (\S+)
Value Required INTERFACE (\S+)
Value Required STATUS (\S+)

Start
  ^VRF\s+Configuration\s*:\s*$$
  ^-+\s*$$
  ^VRF\s+Name\s+:\s+${VRF}\s*$$ -> VrfHeader
  ^\s*$$
  ^. -> Error

VrfHeader
  ^\s+Interfaces\s+Status\s*$$
  ^\s+-+\s*$$ -> Interfaces
  ^VRF\s+Name\s+:\s+${VRF}\s*$$ -> VrfHeader
  ^\s*$$
  ^. -> Error

Interfaces
  ^\s+${INTERFACE}\s+${STATUS}\s*$$ -> Record
  ^VRF\s+Name\s+:\s+${VRF}\s*$$ -> VrfHeader
  ^\s*$$
  ^. -> Error
